name: 22-inch_Andrew_Series_Narrow_On_the_Wall_3.5-inch_Interior_Depth_Cabinet
description:
This narrow cabinet easily mounts in places other cabinets won't fit, including the side of another cabinet. The cabinet mounts on the wall with built-in cleats inside for an easy installation. A recessed white back panel hides the wall inside the cabinet. A beautiful mitered raised panel door sits on concealed hinges. The door is left undrilled for a knob or handle so you can mount it to open either direction. This item is perfect as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet or storage cabinet anywhere. Nearly 3.5 inches of depth exists inside the cabinet area.

Materials: Solid pine, glassFinish: Unfinished pineOne (1) doorTwo (2) shelvesDimensions: 22 inches high x 11 inches wide x 4.25 inches deepMaterialWoodTypeMedicine Cabinet, Wall CabinetFinishNatural Finish
